"Bloom"

Every relationship a person goes through has a lot to do with how they live their lives. Rejection, acceptance, from childhood to adulthood to the age at which clarity begins to permeate. Their minds are formed in a certain form, so please stop judging them.

The only way to learn about peace is to not judge others' ideas about peace.
